uma: UMA (Unraid Management Agent)
uma:
uma: UMA is a comprehensive monitoring and control system for Unraid servers
uma: providing REST API access, WebSocket streaming, and MCP server support.
uma:
uma: Features:
uma: - REST API with OpenAPI 3.0.3 documentation
uma: - Model Context Protocol (MCP) server with 50+ auto-discovered tools
uma: - WebSocket streaming for real-time monitoring
uma: - Optimized logging system for Unraid disk space conservation
uma: - Prometheus metrics integration
uma:
uma: Homepage: https://github.com/domalab/uma
uma:
